# destroy

All documents can be destroyed.

To destroy scrolls, click the BIG RED X on the scroll editor.

Here is a link to the scroll editor, editing the [destroy scroll](scrolls/destroy):

[![](iconsymbols/edit.svg)](scrolleditor.php?scroll=scrolls/destroy)

And here is a direct link to the destroy of scrolls. Instant destruction, no undo.  Everything dies.

[![](iconsymbols/delete.svg)](scrolldelete.html)

Forks can be deleted from [fork.html](fork.html) by turning on delete mode and again instant click for total permanent destruction.